changing board cell [0][2] to 'M' from player 0's perspective would result in the board: 
 x  o  M 
 o  x  . 
 o  x  o 

while changing board cell [0][2] to 'M' from player 1's perspective would result in the board
 o  x  o 
 .  x  o 
 M  o  x 

